---
layout: base
title: "Blog"
description: "Escrevo para organizar ideias, questionar práticas comuns da web e compartilhar aprendizados sobre
acessibilidade, front-end e pensamento crítico."
permalink: "/blog/{% if pagination.pageNumber > 0 %}page/{{ pagination.pageNumber + 1 }}/{% endif %}"
pagination:
  data: collections.posts
  size: 12
---
<div class="h-feed">
  <h1 class="mb-6 p-name font-bold text-2xl">Blog</h1>
  <p>{{ post.data.description }}</p>
  <a class="hidden u-url" href="{{ site.url }}/blog/"></a>

  <div class="space-y-8">
    {% for post in pagination.items %}
      <article class="pb-6 border-b h-entry">
        <h2 class="p-name font-semibold text-xl"><a class="u-url" href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h2>
        <time class="dark:text-gray-400 text-sm dt-published" datetime="{{ post.data.pubDate | toISOString }}">{{ post.data.pubDate | readableDate }}</time>
        <div class="mt-2 p-summary text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
          {{ post.data.description or (post.templateContent | striptags | truncate(160)) }}
        </div>
        <div class="space-x-2 mt-2 text-sm">
          {% for tag in post.data.tags %}
            <a class="bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 p-category px-2 py-0.5 rounded" href="/tags/{{ tag | slug }}/">#{{ tag }}</a>
          {% endfor %}
        </div>
      </article>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</div>

{% if pagination.pages.length > 1 %}
{% include 'components/pagination.njk' %}
{% endif %}